        { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Do they work with nitrile/latex/vinyl gloves?", "answer": "Yes — this is the primary use case. 0.4mm thin, designed to layer inside sealed gloves without affecting fit. Works with nitrile, latex, vinyl, rubber, hockey gloves, ski gloves, and work gloves." } },
